#compdef rofi-emoji
# Documentation: https://github.com/Mange/rofi-emoji
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-20
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above. rofi-emoji is a rofi plugin
# (no standalone binary). Flags below are the rofi-config knobs it
# registers; typically invoked via `rofi -show emoji -modes emoji <opts>`.

_arguments -s -S \
  '-emoji-mode[default action on select]:mode:(insert copy insert_no_copy menu stdout)' \
  '-emoji-file[custom emoji database file]:file:_files' \
  '-emoji-format[custom row formatting]:fmt:' && return 0
